            Doctor Assignment
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Efficient assignment of doctors to patients based on specialization
            and availability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
